title: Super Bowl Gambling and Analytics with Chad Millman & Warren Sharp, plus Brady Quinn/Pete Prisco (Football 1/31)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Pete Prisco in Atlanta to cover all angles of Super Bowl LIII. Then, Chad Millman of The Action Network hops on to discuss gambling storylines ahead of Sunday, and finally, Warren Sharp chats Super Bowl analytics.
